ogle-review-btn" href="https://instantmed.com.au/api/review-redirect?utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=inline_cta&amp;utm_campaign=review" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Leave a Google review</a></div></div><div style="text-align:center;padding:12px 0 0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;margin:16px 0 0 0"><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.6">Know someone who needs this? <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/patient?tab=referrals&amp;utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=referral_cta&amp;utm_campaign=referral" style="color:#2563EB;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none">Give them $5 off and get $5 yourself</a></p></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians