        </style></head><body style="font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#475569;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F8F7F4;color-scheme:light dark;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%" data-x-apple-data-detectors="false"><div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#F8F7F4">✅ Test, your Sildenafil prescription is ready ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌</div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%;background-color:#F8F7F4"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:48px 16px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" class="email-card" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:40px 40px 24px 40px;text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:middle;padding-right:10px"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/logo.png" alt="InstantMed" width="36" height="36" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px"/></td><td style="vertical-align:middle"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/wordmark.png" alt="" width="130" height="auto" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;max-width:130px;height:auto"/></td></tr></tbody></table></a></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0 40px"><div style="border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9"></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-content" style="padding:32px 40px 40px 40px;background-color:#ffffff"><div style="text-align:center;padding:0 0 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#15803D;margin-bottom:12px">✓</div><h1 style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Prescription approved</h1><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8">Sildenafil</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Your prescription for <strong>Sildenafil</strong> has been approved. Your eScript will arrive by SMS shortly. Take your phone to any pharmacy and they&#x27;ll scan the QR code. Bring your Medicare card for any PBS subsidy.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">How to take Sildenafil</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#475569;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Take 30–60 minutes before sexual activity</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Effects typically last 4–6 hours</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Do not take more than one dose (100mg max) in 24 hours</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Works best on an empty stomach. A heavy meal may delay the effect</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">Do NOT take with nitrate medications (e.g. GTN spray). This can cause a dangerous drop in blood pressure</li></ul></div><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#FFFBEB;border:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Important safety information</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#475569;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Common side effects: headache, flushing, nasal congestion, indigestion. These usually pass quickly</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Avoid excessive alcohol. It can reduce effectiveness and increase side effects</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Do NOT combine with nitrate medications or recreational drugs containing nitrates (e.g. poppers)</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">Seek urgent medical attention for chest pain, an erection lasting more than 4 hours, or sudden vision/hearing changes</li></ul></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">View request</a></td></tr></tbody></table><div class="google-review-pill" style="border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;margin:4px 0 0 0;padding:16px 0 4px"><div style="background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:2px;color:#F59E0B;line-height:1">★★★★★</p><p style="margin:0 0 14px 0;font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.5;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">If we saved you a trip to the GP, a quick Google review would mean the world to us.</p><a class="google-review-btn" href="https://instantmed.com.au/api/review-redirect?utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=inline_cta&amp;utm_campaign=review" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Leave a Google review</a></div></div><div style="text-align:center;padding:12px 0 0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;margin:16px 0 0 0"><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.6">Know someone who needs this? <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/patient?tab=referrals&amp;utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=referral_cta&amp;utm_campaign=referral" style="color:#2563EB;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none">Give them $5 off and get $5 yourself</a></p></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;