          }
        </style></head><body style="font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#475569;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F8F7F4;color-scheme:light dark;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%" data-x-apple-data-detectors="false"><div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#F8F7F4">Your Medical Certificate request is with a doctor now 👍 ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌</div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%;background-color:#F8F7F4"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:48px 16px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" class="email-card" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:40px 40px 24px 40px;text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:middle;padding-right:10px"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/logo.png" alt="InstantMed" width="36" height="36" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px"/></td><td style="vertical-align:middle"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/wordmark.png" alt="" width="130" height="auto" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;max-width:130px;height:auto"/></td></tr></tbody></table></a></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0 40px"><div style="border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9"></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-content" style="padding:32px 40px 40px 40px;background-color:#ffffff"><div style="background-color:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 18px;margin-bottom:14px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="width:28px;vertical-align:middle"><div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#1D4ED8;color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;text-align:center">ℹ</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle"><p style="color:#1D4ED8;font-size:14px;margin:0;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4">Request submitted</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request has been submitted. A doctor will review it soon. Most requests are wrapped up within a couple of hours.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><tr><td style="padding:12px 0;color:#64748B;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #F1F5F9">Reference</td><td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;font-family:inherit;text-align:right;color:#1E293B;border-bottom:1px solid #F1F5F9;letter-spacing:inherit">REQ-TEST</td></tr><tr><td style="padding:12px 0;color:#64748B;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #F1F5F9">Status</td><td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;font-family:inherit;text-align:right;color:#1E293B;border-bottom:1px solid #F1F5F9;letter-spacing:inherit">In review</td></tr></div><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">What happens next</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#475569;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">A doctor reviews your request (typically 1–2 hours)</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">You&#x27;ll get an email once a decision is made</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">If anything else is needed, the doctor will reach out</li></ul></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">Track Your Request</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians · 5 ★ on Google</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8