er:1px solid #FDE68A;border-radius:10px;padding:12px 18px;margin-bottom:14px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="width:28px;vertical-align:middle"><div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#92400E;color:#ffffff;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;line-height:22px;text-align:center">!</div></td><td style="vertical-align:middle"><p style="color:#92400E;font-size:14px;margin:0;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4">The doctor has a question</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">The doctor reviewing your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request needs a bit more information before they can move forward.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;color:#92400E">Message from the doctor:</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#78350F;line-height:1.7">Need more info.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">Respond Now</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.6">No rush, but responding soon helps us process your request faster. Your spot in the queue is saved.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians · 5 ★ on Google</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Surry Hills NSW 2010</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
