:0 0 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#FFFBEB;border:1px solid #FDE68A;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#92400E;margin-bottom:12px">💳</div><h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Complete your payment</h1></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test Patient,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">We noticed your previous payment for your Medical Certificate request didn&#x27;t go through. No worries, you can try again using the link below.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td><p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#44403C"><strong style="color:#1C1917">Amount due:</strong> $19.95</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style="text-align:center"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/pay/test" style="display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(37,99,235,0.25);background-color:#2563EB;color:#ffffff">Complete Payment</a></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.6">If you&#x27;re having trouble, ensure your card details are correct and you have sufficient funds. Need help? Just reply to this email.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians · 5 ★ on Google</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Surry Hills NSW 2010</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
