padding:0 0 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#15803D;margin-bottom:12px">✓</div><h1 style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Refund processed</h1><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8">Your payment is being returned</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">We&#x27;ve processed a refund for your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request. The amount will be returned to your original payment method.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">What to expect</h3><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Refunds typically appear within 5–7 business days, depending on your bank or card issuer. If you don&#x27;t see it after 7 business days, contact your bank directly.</p></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:none;background-color:transparent;color:#1E293B;border:1px solid #E2E8F0">View Request Details</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td class="ema