        </style></head><body style="font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#475569;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F8F7F4;color-scheme:light dark;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%" data-x-apple-data-detectors="false"><div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#F8F7F4">We couldn’t help with your Medical Certificate this time. Next steps inside ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌</div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%;background-color:#F8F7F4"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:48px 16px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" class="email-card" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:40px 40px 24px 40px;text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:0 auto"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:middle;padding-right:10px"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/logo.png" alt="InstantMed" width="36" height="36" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:8px"/></td><td style="vertical-align:middle"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/wordmark.png" alt="" width="130" height="auto" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;max-width:130px;height:auto"/></td></tr></tbody></table></a></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0 40px"><div style="border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9"></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-content" style="padding:32px 40px 40px 40px;background-color:#ffffff"><div style="text-align:center;padding:0 0 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#64748B;margin-bottom:12px">\\uD83D\\uDCCB</div><h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">We weren&#x27;t able to help this time</h1></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">We know this isn&#x27;t the result you were hoping for. After carefully reviewing your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request, the doctor wasn&#x27;t able to approve it through our telehealth service on this occasion.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#F0FDF4;border:1px solid #BBF7D0;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Full refund guaranteed</h3><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Your payment will be refunded in full to your original payment method within 5–7 business days. No action needed on your end.</p></div><div style="margin:20px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1E293B;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">What you can do next</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#475569;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">See your regular GP for an in-person assessment</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">Call 13SICK (13 7425) for after-hours GP advice</li></ul></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6;margin-top:20px">We&#x27;re sorry we couldn&#x27;t help this time, Test. We&#x27;re always here if you need us down the track.</p><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:none;background-color:transparent;color:#1E293B;border:1px solid #E2E8F0">View request details</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians · 5 ★ on Google</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Surry Hills NSW 2010</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
