r;padding:0 0 20px"><div style="display:inline-block;width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:50%;background-color:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;line-height:48px;text-align:center;font-size:22px;color:#1D4ED8;margin-bottom:12px">⏳</div><h1 style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:-0.4px;line-height:1.4;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Still on it</h1><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8">Your Medical Certificate is nearly done</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:15px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> is taking a little longer than usual, but we&#x27;re still on it. Our doctor is working through the queue and will have your review done shortly.</p><div class="email-box" style="background-color:#EFF6FF;border:1px solid #BFDBFE;border-radius:10px;padding:16px 20px;margin:14px 0"><p style="margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">We&#x27;ll email you the moment it&#x27;s done. No action needed on your end.</p></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:16px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/track/REQ-TEST" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:none;background-color:transparent;color:#1E293B;border:1px solid #E2E8F0">Check your request</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-