5px;color:#475569;line-height:1.6">Here&#x27;s your verification code. Enter it where prompted to continue:</p><div class="email-code-block" style="background-color:#F5F7F9;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 12px;margin:12px 0;text-align:center"><p aria-label="Verification code: 0 0 0 0 0 0" style="margin:0;font-size:15px;font-family:&#x27;SF Mono&#x27;, &#x27;Fira Code&#x27;, Consolas, monospace;font-weight:700;color:#1E293B;letter-spacing:3px">000000</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94A3B8;line-height:1.6">This code expires in 10 minutes. Keep it to yourself, we won&#x27;t ask for it by email or phone.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:0;border-top:1px solid #F1F5F9;background-color:#F8F7F4"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:20px 40px;text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:12px;color:#64748B;line-height:1.8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E2E8F0">·</span><a href="__UNSUBSCRIBE_URL__" style="color:#64748B;text-decoration:none">Manage preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">Made with care in Australia 🌤️ · Trusted by 500+ Australians · 5 ★ on Google</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#94A3B8;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334 · Level 1/457-459 Elizabeth St, Su